label: uncl7383
comment: Code specifying the surface or layer of an object.

values.label: Side one
values.comment: The location is side one.

values.label: Side two
values.comment: The location is side two.

values.label: On surface
values.comment: To indicate that the entity being specified is on the surface.

values.label: Off surface
values.comment: To indicate that the entity being specified is off the surface.

values.label: Soluble
values.comment: Specifies that the surface/layer/position being described is the soluble portion.

values.label: Opposite corners
values.comment: The surface or layer of the product being described is the opposite corners.

values.label: Corner Diagonals
values.comment: The surface or layer of the product being described are the corner diagonals.

values.label: Port
values.comment: The left-hand side (looking forward) of a ship, boat or aircraft.

values.label: Starboard
values.comment: The right-hand side (looking forward) of a ship, boat or aircraft.

values.label: Tooth facial surface
values.comment: Surface of a tooth directed toward the face and opposite the lingual surface.

values.label: Tooth incisal surface
values.comment: Surface of the tooth relating to the cutting edge of the anterior teeth, incisors or canines.

values.label: Tooth distal surface
values.comment: Surface of the tooth toward the back of the dental arch, or away from the midline.

values.label: Tooth buccal surface
values.comment: Surface of the tooth pertaining to or around the cheek.

values.label: Tooth occlusal surface
values.comment: Surface of the tooth pertaining to the masticating surfaces of the posterior teeth.

values.label: Tooth lingual surface
values.comment: Surface of the tooth pertaining to or around the tongue.

values.label: Tooth mesial surface
values.comment: Surface of the tooth toward the midline of the dental arch.

values.label: Back of cab
values.comment: The location is at the back of the cab.

values.label: Both sides
values.comment: The location is both sides.

values.label: Bottom
values.comment: The location is on the bottom.

values.label: Dual fuel tank positions
values.comment: The location is in the dual fuel tank positions.

values.label: Front
values.comment: The location is in the front.

values.label: Inside
values.comment: The location is in the inside.

values.label: Left
values.comment: The location is on the left.

values.label: Overall
values.comment: The location is overall.

values.label: One side
values.comment: The location is on one side.

values.label: Outside
values.comment: The location is on the outside.

values.label: Right
values.comment: The location is on the right.

values.label: Rear
values.comment: The location is in the rear.

values.label: Spare tyre position
values.comment: The location is the spare tyre position.

values.label: Tank bottom
values.comment: The location is at the tank bottom.

values.label: Top
values.comment: The location is on the top.

values.label: Two sides
values.comment: The location is on two sides.

values.label: Under cab
values.comment: The location is under the cab.
